(94, 'SS12.11', 'Simple concrete ramp (median total cost)', '384.00', 2010, 'Unit Costs of Health and Social Care 2011 (Curtis, 2011), p.93', 'http://www.pssru.ac.uk/pdf/uc/uc2011/uc2011.pdf', 'High', 'The source quotes the median cost, as the range of values derived from local authorities was wide (£66 - £2,734), and the mean (£646) was distorted by the wide range.  The source also provides an annuitised cost (and gives information on how this has been derived) - the median annual equipment cost for a simple concrete ramp is £46.  The original data are old, but the source comments that they have been substantiated by cross-referencing with more recent costs.', 7, 2, 8, 50, 1, NULL),
(95, 'SS12.12', 'Grab rail (median total cost)', '52.00', 2010, 'Unit Costs of Health and Social Care 2011 (Curtis, 2011), p.93', 'http://www.pssru.ac.uk/pdf/uc/uc2011/uc2011.pdf', 'High', 'The source quotes the median cost, as the range of values derived from local authorities was wide (£4 - £422), and the mean (£94) was distorted by the wide range.  The source also provides an annuitised cost (and gives information on how this has been derived) - the median annual equipment cost for a grab rail is £6.  The original data are old, but the source comments that they have been substantiated by cross-referencing with more recent costs.', 7, 2, 8, 50, 1, NULL),
