(182, 'E&E1.8', 'Job Seeker''s Allowance\nCost of processing each new claim for JSA', '114.00', 2009, 'DWP Annual Report and Accounts 2010-11, p10', '', 'Medium', 'Provisional (lower) costs for 2010-11 also available.  Includes administrative expenditure on pay and staff pension costs, current expenditure on goods and services, and capital depreciation.  Excludes one-off expenditure (cost of investment and other one-off charges).  Direct and apportioned indirect costs are included, such as staff, IT, estates, management and corporate support costs', 3, 10, 4, 39, 20, NULL),
