(251, 'E&S2.0.3', 'Permanent exclusion from school - crime, per individual per effective year (see comments)', '970.44', 2005, 'Misspent Youth (2007)', 'http://www.thinknpc.org/publications/misspent-youth/', 'Medium', 'Note age of data.  Per effective year figure is based on BMJ study 18 years costs, i.e. the total effective lifetime figure divided by 16. ', 2, 23, 12, NULL, 50, 248),
